Back Story

The Podgonauts have found themselves in a very spicy situation, they've run into the planet of Sriracha! Not knowing their own spice levels, the poor sods have decided to try a bit.. to amusing results! (tad too spicy!) That'll teach 'em! Podgonaut Edition C comes in the form of the Panda Exploration Corp, dressed in a sriracha jumpsuit each with a laser engraved disc embedded in their chest. They also have articulated head and removable dome.

name: Monkey Podgonauts Edition A - resin collab with Cris Rose
description:
[Goes on sale Friday October 26th at 18:00 London time GMT+1]

Colour: Jumpsuit orange Run: Edition of 3 Materials: Resin, Acrylic Size: 3" x 3.5" x 3.5" Weight: 250g Articulation: Head, removable dome

Back Story

The Bigwigs over at Podgonauts HQ are in a bit of a pickle. The Panda Podgonauts which have been deployed over the past 6 months or so have yet to return with food samples from their adventures, which makes the head honchos nervous with their choice to rely on the Pandas in the first place.. And what do you do when you can't rely on your highly skilled and trained astronaut Pandas? Rely on your mechanics instead (or in this case.. the Monkeys). Equipped in their jumpsuits, (and their booster seats.. 'cos these guys are really short) They're raring to go, ready to pick up the slack. Huge shoes to fill boys. Huge shoes indeed Monkey Podgonaut Edition A's comes in the form of 3 members of the Monkey Exploration Corp, dressed in a 'Jumpsuit Orange' jumpsuit each with a laser engraved disc embedded in their chest. They also have articulated head and removable dome. All this for the great price of $120usd!
